Gallery+ Block Installation

If you have a pre-existing install of Gallery+ Block, you will need to deactivate it before activating this one.

INSTALL: 
1. Locate the Gallery+ zip file
2. Go to your WordPress dashboard. Plugins, Add New, Upload and select the Gallery+ zip file.
3. Once uploaded, click activate


SUPPORT & DOCUMENTATION:
If you are looking for detailed documentation, please visit http://pizazzwp.com/gallery-user-guide/
If you require support, please visit http://support.pizazzwp.com